<h3>Fan</h3>
<p>The SmartThings Fan platform lets you control devices that have fan-related capabilities. For a SmartThings device to be represented by the fan platform, it must have one or more of the capabilities below in addition to the <a href="https://smartthings.developer.samsung.com/develop/api-ref/capabilities.html#Switch"><code>switch</code></a> capability.</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Capability</th>
<th>Fan Features</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><a href="https://smartthings.developer.samsung.com/develop/api-ref/capabilities.html#Fan-Speed"><code>fanSpeed</code></a></td>
<td><code>speed</code> (<code>off</code>, <code>low</code>, <code>medium</code>, and <code>high</code>)</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
