<h3>Lock</h3>
<p>The SmartThings Lock platform lets you control devices that have the <a href="https://smartthings.developer.samsung.com/develop/api-ref/capabilities.html#Lock"><code>lock</code></a> capability, showing current lock status and supporting lock and unlock commands.</p>
